      <lg type="song lyrics">
        <head>Song For Me</head>
        <lg number="1" type="stanza">
          <l>When I go, </l>
          <l>You'll write a song for me </l>
          <l>Now the words come out so easily </l>
          <l>You've kept them locked, </l>
          <l>But now you see </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="2" type="stanza">
          <l>That what you've known, </l>
          <l>Has changed in just one day, </l>
          <l>Oh the one you thought was here to stay </l>
          <l>Turned feather clouds of yesterday </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="3" type="stanza">
          <l>I'm taking time </l>
          <l>I have to make it mine </l>
          <l>I'll take the time </l>
          <l>I'll go a way to find you </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="4" type="stanza">
          <l>When it will be over, </l>
          <l>I'll come to you again </l>
          <l>When my words get broken, </l>
          <l>Nothing is true to me </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="5" type="stanza">
          <l>That's how I'll know </l>
          <l>What's right or wrong for me </l>
          <l>Sleeping days won't set me free </l>
          <l>I'll find a way, so I could be </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="6" type="stanza">
          <l>Taking the time </l>
          <l>I have to make it mine </l>
          <l>I'll take the time </l>
          <l>I'll find myself, </l>
          <l>To find you.</l>
        </lg>
      </lg>
    </body>
